4. -113 - 37
1s Complement
(-01110001) (113)
- 00100101  (37)
----------
  10001110 // 113 in 1s Complement
- 00100101
----------
  10001110
+ 11011010 // 1s Complement von 37
----------
 101101000 // Mit Carry
  01101000+1 // Carry addieren
----------
  01101001 // Overflow!

2s Complement
(-01110001) (113)
- 00100101  (37)
----------
  10001111 // 113 in 2s Complement
- 00100101
----------
  10001111
+(11011010 + 1)
----------
  10001111
+ 11011011 // 37 in 2s Complement
----------
 101101010
  01101010 // Ohne Carry -> Overflow!









































